      "display_title": "Issue #1671: [Slicing] Redesign Add Promo Code Form + Live Preview",
      "main_description_html": "<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Type:</strong> Slicing (frontend build) · <strong>Epic:</strong> Add promo (<code class=\"notranslate\">/promocodes/add</code>) · ref <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4611365101\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1660\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1660/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1660\">#1660</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Rebuild <code class=\"notranslate\">promocode-form.component</code> (add mode) markup (design: <code class=\"notranslate\">PromoCodeEdit.html</code> / <code class=\"notranslate\">addpromocodes.png</code>).</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Scope:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">.form-card</code> sections (Details / Product &amp; discount / Duration &amp; limits / Restrict to a user) + <code class=\"notranslate\">.form-summary</code> <strong>live preview</strong>.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Decision (brainstorm §1):</strong> <strong>real API fields only</strong> — discount type <strong>Percentage / Amount</strong> (no Free trial), billing <strong>Monthly / Yearly / Both</strong> (no Lifetime), duration once/forever/repeating. <strong>Drop the custom Code + Generate input</strong> (code is server-generated → show it read-only after save).</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Acceptance:</strong> preview mirrors inputs; name rule (≤20, alphanumeric+space); no design-only inputs that don't persist.</p>\n<hr>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Part of the <strong>Support Console</strong> redesign (Clients + Promo Codes CRUD).</em><br>\n<em>Refs: <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/plan.md</code> · <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/brainstorm.md</code>. Related: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4609472943\" data-permission-text