      "display_title": "Issue #1672: [Integration] Wire Add Promo Code Form To API",
      "main_description_html": "<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Type:</strong> Integration (wiring) · <strong>Epic:</strong> Add promo (<code class=\"notranslate\">/promocodes/add</code>) · ref <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4611365101\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1660\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1660/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1660\">#1660</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Wire the add form to the existing promo API.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Scope:</strong> API-driven <strong>product types</strong> (<code class=\"notranslate\">getProductSupport</code>), <strong>allowed-user picker</strong> (<code class=\"notranslate\">getListUsers</code>, single email), build the <code class=\"notranslate\">addPromoCode</code> payload (<code class=\"notranslate\">percent_off</code>/<code class=\"notranslate\">amount_off</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">duration</code>/<code class=\"notranslate\">duration_in_months</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">expires_on</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">max_redemptions</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">metadata.applicable_products</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">allowed_user</code>). Server generates the code.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Acceptance:</strong> create persists; returns to list with refresh; validation + error toasts intact.</p>\n<hr>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Part of the <strong>Support Console</strong> redesign (Clients + Promo Codes CRUD).</em><br>\n<em>Refs: <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/plan.md</code> · <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/brainstorm.md</code>. Related: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4609472943\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1