      "display_title": "Issue #1673: [Slicing] Redesign Edit Promo Code Form (Read-Only Except Name)",
      "main_description_html": "<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Type:</strong> Slicing (frontend build) · <strong>Epic:</strong> Edit promo (<code class=\"notranslate\">/promocodes/edit/:code/:promo_id</code>) · ref <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4611366311\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1661\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1661/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1661\">#1661</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Reuse the Add form layout for edit mode (title \"Edit promo code\").</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Decision (brainstorm §1b):</strong> <strong>all fields read-only except Promo code name</strong> — matches <code class=\"notranslate\">_disableAllInput(['name'])</code>; the backend only updates the name. Present the full config read-only so support can see it.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Acceptance:</strong> only Name is editable; other fields visibly read-only; layout matches Add.</p>\n<hr>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Part of the <strong>Support Console</strong> redesign (Clients + Promo Codes CRUD).</em><br>\n<em>Refs: <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/plan.md</code> · <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/brainstorm.md</code>. Related: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4609472943\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1658\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1658/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1658\">#1658</a>–<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4611367469\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662\" data-hovercard-ty