    {
      "anchor_id": "issue-gothrumedia-villume-admin-1678",
      "display_title": "Issue #1678: Restyle reset-token loading to centered spinner",
      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">Problem</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">The reset-token page (<code class=\"notranslate\">/resettoken</code>) shows a plain <code class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p&gt;Loading...&lt;/p&gt;</code> text while it clears the existing session token and redirects. Looks unpolished.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Goal</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Replace the plain text with an animated spinner, centered vertically and horizontally on the screen.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Scope</h2>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><code class=\"notranslate\">src/app/pages/reset-password/reset-token/reset-token.component.html</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"notranslate\">src/app/pages/reset-password/reset-token/reset-token.component.scss</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance</h2>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Spinner animates while the page processes/redirects.</li>\n<li>Spinner is centered on the full screen viewport.</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\">🤖 Generated with <a href=\"https://claude.com/claude-code\" rel=\"nofollow\">Claude Code</a></p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo by Developer</h2>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" data-component=\"Octicon\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-device-camera-video\">\n    <path d=\"M16 3.75v8.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.136.643L11 10.575v.675A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 13h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 11.25v-6.5C0 3.784.784 3 1.75 3h7.5c.966 0 1.75.784 1.75 1.75v.675l3.864-2.318A.75.75 0 0 1 16 3.75Zm-6.5 1a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25h-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v6.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-6.5ZM11 8.825l3.5 2.1v-5.85l-3.5 2.1Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n    <span class=\"m-1\">2026-06-19.14-51-59.mp4</span>\n    <span class=\"dropdown-caret\"></span>\n  </summary>\n\n  <video src=\"videos/video-8889b1fb-ece7-45fe-9acf-062028ece2d0.mp4\" data-canonical-src=\"videos/video-8889b1fb-ece7-45fe-9acf-06