    {
      "anchor_id": "issue-gothrumedia-villume-admin-1670",
      "display_title": "Issue #1670: [Integration] Wire Promo Delete Modal To Endpoint",
      "main_description_html": "<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Type:</strong> Integration (wiring) · <strong>Epic:</strong> Delete promo (<code class=\"notranslate\">/promocodes</code>) · ref <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4611367469\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662\">#1662</a></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Wire the modal's confirm to the existing delete endpoint.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Scope:</strong> <code class=\"notranslate\">deletePromoCode(code)</code>; on success remove the row + refresh count + toast; handle error states.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><strong>Acceptance:</strong> delete persists via the existing endpoint; Cancel aborts; no orphaned UI state.</p>\n<hr>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Part of the <strong>Support Console</strong> redesign (Clients + Promo Codes CRUD).</em><br>\n<em>Refs: <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/plan.md</code> · <code class=\"notranslate\">docs/15-06-2026/brainstorm.md</code>. Related: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4609472943\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1658\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1658/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1658\">#1658</a>–<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4611367469\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/villume-admin/issues/1662\">#1662</a> (Project 32).</em></p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Demo by Developer</h2>\n<details open=\"\" class=\"details-reset border rounded-2\">\n  <summary class=\"tmp-px-3 py-2\">\n    <svg aria-hidden=\"true\" data-component=\"Octicon\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" data-view-component=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-device-camera-video\">\n    <path d=\"M16 3.75v8.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.136.643L11 10.575v.675A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 9.25 13h-7.5A1.75 1.75 0 0 1 0 11.25v-6.5C0 3.784.784 3 1.75 3h7.5c.966 0 1.75.784 1.75 1.75v.675l3.864-2.318A.75.75 0 0 1 16 3.75Zm-6.5 1a.25.25 0 0 0-.25-.25h-7.5a.25.25 0 0 0-.25.25v6.5c0 .138.112.25.25.25h7.5a.25.25 0 0 0 .25-.25v-6.5ZM11 8.825l3.5 2.1v-5.85l-3.5 2.1Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n    <span class=\"m-1\">2026-06-19.14-55-51.mp4</span>\n    <span class=\"dropdown-caret\"></span>\n  </summary>\n\n  <video src=\"videos/video-9fc74f91-7e2a-4577-a738-3840ad34d81c.mp4\" data-canonical-src=\"videos/video-9fc74f91-7e2a-4577-a738-3840ad34d81c.mp4\" controls=\"controls\" muted=\"muted\" class=\"d-block rounded-bottom-2 border-top width-fit\" style=\"max-height:640px; min-height: 200px\">\n\n  </video>\n</details>\n",
